La Tour Eiffel via @dapper_drinks ⠀
⠀
Double Tap you you want one come 5pm!⠀
⠀
2½ oz @hinecognacs Cognac⠀
½ oz @cointreau Orange Liqueur⠀
½ oz Suze⠀
1 Barspoon of @stgeorgespirits Absinthe⠀
.⠀
Combine all ingredients, except the absinthe, in a mixing glass with ice. Stir till chilled. Rinse the inside of a chilled champagne flute with the absinthe or spritz the inside with an atomizer. Strain the contents of the mixing glass into the rinsed flute. Garnish with a lemon twist. Serve.⠀

Scotch Chocolate via @dapper_drinks ⠀
⠀
Double Tap if this looks delicious!⠀
⠀
⠀
7-8 oz Hot Chocolate⠀
¾ oz @johnniewalker Blended Scotch⠀
¼ oz @ardbeg_usa Islay Scotch⠀
¼ oz @amaromonte Montenegro Amaro⠀
⠀
Pour your favorite hot chocolate into a warmed mug and stir in the rest of ingredients. Grate some fresh cinnamon and sprinkle some chocolate over the top. Garnish with a roasted marshmallow and a charred cinnamon stick if you're feeling crazy. Serve.⠀
